title: Chicken and Bean Chilli
ingredients: ['1 tablespoon vegetable oil', '1 onion, chopped', '3 cloves garlic, crushed', '1/2 (220g) tin diced jalapeno peppers', '1 (130g) tin chopped green chillies', '2 teaspoons ground cumin', '1 teaspoon dried oregano', '1 teaspoon ground cayenne pepper', '825ml chicken stock', '375g cooked chicken breast, chopped', '3 (410g) tins cannellini beans', '115g Cheddar cheese, grated']
